%% seq_09_skill_profile.mmd
%% Scope: Profile surface overview only.
%% Detail files:
%%   - seq_09a_profile_views_skills.mmd
%%   - seq_09b_profile_snapshot_sharing.mmd
%% Runtime notes:
%%   - /profile loads profile, spider charts, delivery metrics, featured reviews, current snapshot
%%   - profile surface now includes snapshot publish/history/access/rotate-link flows
%%   - recruiter_bookmarks still has no active route/controller surface

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor O as Profile Owner
    actor V as Viewer
    participant UI as Browser / Frontend
    participant Profile as Profile Controllers
    participant Skills as Skill Controllers
    participant Snap as Snapshot Controllers
    participant App as Queries / Commands

    O->>UI: Open /profile
    UI->>Profile: GET /profile
    Profile->>App: load profile aggregate
    App-->>Profile: user + completeness + spider charts + delivery + featured reviews + current snapshot
    Profile-->>UI: Render owner profile workspace

    O->>UI: Add/update/remove skills
    UI->>Skills: POST / PUT / DELETE /profile/skills/*
    Skills->>App: mutate user_skills
    Skills-->>UI: Redirect or updated state

    O->>UI: Publish/manage profile snapshots
    UI->>Snap: POST / GET / PATCH /profile/snapshots/*
    Snap->>App: publish / read current / read history / update access / rotate link
    Snap-->>UI: Snapshot control state

    V->>UI: Open /users/:id/profile
    UI->>Profile: GET /users/:id/profile
    Profile->>App: load public profile aggregate
    App-->>Profile: public-facing profile data
    Profile-->>UI: Render public profile with charts and highlights

    V->>UI: Open /profiles/:slug?token=...
    UI->>Snap: GET public snapshot route
    Snap->>App: resolve public snapshot by slug (+ optional token)
    Snap-->>UI: Return shareable snapshot payload
